data.value: Malicious Goats In the year of our lord ( or lords (or not (whatever you choose to believe or not to believe in really (we are inclusive))), a band of four young (and some not as young) hot whippersnapper, one of whom was apparently quite horny, decided to assemble and to ram head first the main problems of modern civilisation, one at the time. From the 4 corners of far away Mauricie and Lanaudière, Benoit, Manu, Toma and Vincent assembled under the name Malicious Goats to try and preserve humanity from it’s own folly.
